{"tid":2276094,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"WJSN璉靜曬照驚見「打臉毛澤東」遭罵辱華！　Sana衰掃颱風尾","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T01:39:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"330403979c054f3b2555aecc429173b44fa880fd","tid":2276094,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"南韓藝人「辱華」爭議再添一樁！女團宇宙少女（WJSN）成員璉靜曾曬出在首爾一家咖啡廳的照片，被眼尖的大陸網友發現背景有著一張「毛澤東被打臉」的藝術照，因此氣得出征她的Instagram，就連當時跟她一起合照的TWICE成員Sana也被拖下水，而得知引發爭議後，目前該組照片已經遭刪除。<br />\n<br />\n璉靜8月時上傳了一組照片，照片中可看到她站在首爾一網美咖啡廳打卡拍照，手上還拿著與好友Sana的合照，看似沒有問題的一組照片，卻被部分大陸網友抓出，背景牆上隱約反射出毛澤東的畫像，而且毛澤東臉上還有明顯巴掌印，消息傳回陸網後迅速引來砲火，大陸網友大量湧入她的帳號留言，指稱她「辱華」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5255/d5255546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5255%2Fd5255546.jpg&h=678b422a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲璉靜8月上傳的一組照片遭出征，目前照片已刪除。（圖／翻攝微博）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸網友紛紛砲轟「韓國人集體犯賤嗎」、「限韓令永久鎖死」、「賺人民幣的時候仔細看看鈔票上的人像吧」等，雖有粉絲出面緩頰，但仍遭批評「追星之前先做個人吧」，戰火相當激烈，甚至連Sana也慘遭出征。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5255/d5255547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5255%2Fd5255547.jpg&h=ab2142b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實上，近期發生了多起南韓藝人引發大陸網友不滿的事件，先是李孝利取限定團藝名時，希望能有「毛」字，遭指對毛澤東不敬，接著防彈少年團日前發表韓戰70周年感言時，因感謝韓美兩國共同經歷戰爭、無數男女慘痛犧牲，也挑起對岸極端網友敏感神經，以及近期女星金高銀提到在大陸求學時，國一才學ABCD，且是回到南韓後才第一次看到水性筆，也讓許多網友歸類在「辱華」言論。"},{"pid":"4bdade11fea808f37831d2a978ae94761232c78b","tid":2276094,"uid":161174,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1682054380669e2429bbfc72595074f4fef19fe","tid":2276094,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4bdade11fea808f37831d2a978ae94761232c78b","tid":2276094,"uid":161174,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"就黎全世界都辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fd5daba435a7c345b5297d5055438e47882d10","tid":2276094,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"原來Sana都係黃<br />\n溫屎很自豪"},{"pid":"2580efe46f6cdc32b998d824b5f60403ae338d00","tid":2276094,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFVm4su.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFVm4su.jpg&h=effe392b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dc0b74c9851a3c0803a7d879f2ceb1fbaf78036","tid":2276094,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53fd5daba435a7c345b5297d5055438e47882d10","tid":2276094,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"原來Sana都係黃<br />\n溫屎很自豪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"TWICE全部黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38340e22e6026c57f452e22c88eb606eafbb4f4d","tid":2276094,"uid":152934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"我地毛主席批林批孔 大鳴大放 而家中國強大了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoL2OU9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoL2OU9.png&h=87b8675f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9074ae26cb8c34767fa8beb3090323b8ce7edbc7","tid":2276094,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dc0b74c9851a3c0803a7d879f2ceb1fbaf78036","tid":2276094,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53fd5daba435a7c345b5297d5055438e47882d10","tid":2276094,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"原來Sana都係黃<br />\n溫屎很自豪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"TWICE全部黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"支持twice即係支持你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/d